     C                     MOVE '0'       WSKKB   1        ﾆｬｮf有効hﾎﾞ]
     C           KEY1      CHAINOABPL011             21
     C           *IN21     IFEQ '0'
     C           OBSKJY    ANDEQ'D'
     C           OBSKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     21
     C                     END
     C           *IN21     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE '0'       WTSKB            jbﾆｭchﾎﾞ]
     C           OBAPHZ    IFGT *DATE
     C                     MOVE OBKKBN    WSKKB            ﾆｬｮfﾏcﾃchﾎﾞ]
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE OBSKBN    WSKKB            ﾆｬｮfﾏcﾃchﾎﾞ]
     C                     END
     C                     END
